### Story 2.2 - User Registration Tests

### Test 1: Valid Registration
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@gcredit.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe"
}

### Test 2: Duplicate Email (should return 409)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@gcredit.com",
  "password": "AnotherPass123",
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Smith"
}

### Test 3: Weak Password (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "jane.doe@gcredit.com",
  "password": "weak",
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Doe"
}

### Test 4: Invalid Email Format (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "not-an-email",
  "password": "SecurePass123",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User"
}

### Test 5: Missing Required Field (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@gcredit.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123",
  "lastName": "User"
}
